{
  "stem": "26111.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the usual-- I mean, it was just so full of stereotypes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It is just incredible, nowadays, to even think about.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there was a-- the, the head of that was Streicher, who, I'm happy to say, was hanged after the Nuremberg trials.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the-- there were others-- other things of that same kind.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was hit in a very-- in a very-- we were somewhat insulated, I will say this because my father had his psychoanalytic practice.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were not-- it wasn't exclusively Jewish, by any means.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But he-- and he was trying to, to get more, of course.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was a very difficult time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We were living off capital, as I later learned.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "My mother had her art.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "At that time, you could still go to theaters-- Jews could still go theaters and enjoy-- participate in the-- in the cultural pursuits.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And there were many in Berlin still at that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I happen to love opera and theater, also.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But I went to the opera house quite often and concerts-- Berlin Philharmonic and so on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I was 12 and 13 at the time, so this was-- these were very impressionable years.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And one time, in '38-- this was prior to the Kristallnacht, I remember-- was an opera performance that I very much wanted to see.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the curtain-- there was a delay in the curtain going up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I was in my seat-- or, rather, standing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I had standing room.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I obviously didn't enough money to buy a seat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I was standing up on the-- on the-- top floor.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
